data.description: Price Improvement! VACATION at Home! Extraordinary timeless classic home built in the 1930's updated w/modern amenities. This fully renovated 3 BR, one bath haven epitomizes the essence of Napa living. Nestled on a prime corner lot, central location puts downtown Napa just blocks away. Brimming w/character & infused w/modern charm, practically everything here sparkles w/newness! Make an appointment to see! Roof, siding, bathroom to wall textures, & the gleaming hardwood floors, all rejuvenated. Enjoy toasty fires from the cozy living room. The fully remodeled kitchen boasts brand new appliances including Refrigerator, 5 burner gas stove, new light fixtures; plus a permitted 3-bedroom addition ideal for extra living space/den for watching the latest in entertainment, utilize as a home office, workout space etc. LG full size stacked laundry washer/dryer unit & most furnishings available for $35K separately or make offer. Picture yourself on the private deck or new patio, sipping wine on fall nights, basking in the warm glow of lights & outdoor firepit. Convenient RV parking & clean-out next to the garage for added parking for boat or RV. This isn't just a home; it's a lifestyle waiting for you. Seize this rare  opportunity to own in Napa Valley! Pls allow up to 45 days to close.
